 0:02.72 [...]/sources/firefox-140.10.0/gfx/skia/skia/modules/skcms/src/Transform_inl.h:160:12: error: use of undeclared identifier '__builtin_ia32_vcvtph2ps256'; did you mean '__builtin_ia32_cvtpd2ps256'?
